### ‚ö†Ô∏è Note on Key Management
Currently, private keys are stored in Firebase **only for prototype/demo purposes**.  
For production, ZeroxWallet will move to a fully **non-custodial model** where keys stay only on the client-side (localStorage/secure storage)
